# Next.js Project Architecture

## Directory Structure

- /src/app: Next.js app router. don't define funciton itself for page component, only import. ref: [page.tsx](mdc:apps/app/src/app/(dynamic)/new/page.tsx)
- /src/app/api/ai: Vercel AI SDK routes. ref: [route.ts](mdc:apps/app/src/app/api/ai/generate-additional-tasks/route.ts)
- /src/components: shared components
- /src/hooks: shared react hooks
- /src/utils: shared utilities
- /src/pages/[pageName]: modules for specific page
- /src/pages/[pageName]/[PageName].tsx: page component. ref: [Home.tsx](mdc:apps/app/src/pages/home/Home.tsx)